		<title><![CDATA[Live your #travelgoals in Alaska with UnCruise Adventures]]></title>
		<teaser><![CDATA[UnCruise<sup>&reg;</sup>]]></teaser>
		<lead><![CDATA[
			Adventure is our name and it&rsquo;s our passion. Uncover playgrounds that offer the richest, wildest experiences by hike, paddle, and with locals.
		]]></lead>
		<body><![CDATA[
			<p>Step into tiny worlds and soak in big skies in Alaska&rsquo;s green playground. Let painted mountains set the stage for your explorations. Within our routes we're ready to turn, pause, and seize opportunity. Linger for whale sprays and bow riding dolphins. How will you define adventure?</p>

			<p><strong>Active</strong> [ak&middot;tiv] Mountain-goat scrambles, hours-long kayaking, slow and inquisitive snorkeling... Excursions are as hard-charging or as slow-paced as you like.</p>

			<p><strong>Bushwhacking</strong> [bush&middot;wak&middot;ing] No trail; To attempt a wild and woolly hike in Alaska that typically involves deer trails, bear scat, muskeg, and climbing over logs and through brush.</p>

			<p><strong>Connection</strong> [kuh&middot;nek&middot;shuhn] Meet your people. Small ships acquaint you with like-minded travelers and places that tug your heartstrings. Bonds are hard to define but easy to spot hugging it out at the end&mdash;from co-explorers to friends for life.</p>

			<p><strong>Inclusive</strong> [in&middot;kloo&middot;siv] Excursions, adventure equipment, transfers, baggage handling, and yes, all food and beverages (alcohol too), even heart-tugging photos from your trip are covered in the fare. Truly no hidden costs.</p>

			<p><strong>Small ships</strong> [smaal ships] Laid back; 22-86 guests. That's it. You get to know your travel comrades quickly, and yet there's always a quiet corner or empty space on the bow to scout for wildlife and take it all in.</p>

			<figure class="article-tile">
				<img class="img-responsive" src="https://www.ensembletravel.com/assets/img/ezine/20/02/article/advertorial-05-01.jpg">
			<figure><br>

